          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve detailed information about meters associated with a specific property in a billing system. It queries multiple tables within the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema to gather comprehensive data about meters, including their status, account details, and energy delivery type, filtered by a given property identifier."
